title: Livesey-More Understanding New Age(Antichrist&Occult)(1990)
description: This is Roy Livesey&#039;s amazing book More Understanding the New Age - Discerning Antichrist and the Occult Revival (1990) which identifies numerous ways individuals are deceived in the various New Age religions and exposes New Age centers and their leaders. The move towards a one-world faith has been steadily growing in size as the New World Order slowly gains enough political and financial control to take over the whole planet. The author lays bare the short history of New Age and its occult practices with special emphasis on Christians and their role in this spiritual battle. Find out what is hiding behind all these new religions that are springing out of nowhere every day. 150 pages. A must read for everyone.
